# API Invariants

Laravel 12 module-first ‚Äî repo **`api/`**, code **`src/`**. Read `src/make_help.md` before creating classes.

## Layer

`Controller` ‚Üí `Request` / `Action` / `Query` / `Resource` ‚Üí `Model`

- Controller: thin traits only
- Action: mutate + relationship sync
- Query: search/detail, filters/sorts/includes
- Service: cross-domain or external only ‚Äî not CRUD with Eloquent relation
- OpenAPI source is YAML ‚Äî no Laravel OpenAPI decorators

## Entity

Platform / Tenant / pivot M-N (no model). Detail: `.cursor/extracts/entity-relationship.md`

## Media

S3/public: path in DB, URL at response. Detail: `.cursor/extracts/media-s3.md`

## Code size (soft)

File/class ~**200** lines ¬∑ method ~**20** lines ‚Äî split when exceeded. Detail: `api-code-size.mdc` (glob).

## Codegen

Use `m:*` / `add:*` generators ‚Äî no hand scaffold when generator exists. Detail: `.cursor/extracts/codegen.md`

